9 AS INTRODUCED
10 A Resolution designating April 2026 as Library Month
in the State of Oklahoma.
11
12
13
14 WHEREAS, libraries of all types, including school, public,
15 academic, and special libraries, serve as essential institutions
16 that provide equitable access to information, ideas, and resources
17 in both print and digital formats for people of all ages; and
18 WHEREAS, libraries play a critical role in promoting literacy
19 and lifelong learning by offering robust collections, early literacy
20 programs, and educational services that support school readiness and
21 academic achievement; and
22 WHEREAS, libraries foster a love of reading and intellectual
23 exploration by providing welcoming spaces, knowledgeable staff, and
24
